<tbody>
<tr>
<td>Transactional</td>
<td>"homes for sale in Scottsdale under $500k"</td>
<td>Buy now</td>
<td>Medium</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Informational</td>
<td>"first-time homebuyer guide Arizona"</td>
